{"tid":730469,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愈傳愈盛！C朗經理人急見佩雷斯","createTime":"2018-07-05T12:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:57:40.000Z","uid":33799,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa70c7c1cc44e2276f2986b36d70d9c4d3719bf","tid":730469,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:17:04.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度的經理人文迪斯，已飛赴馬德里見會長佩雷斯，預料這匆匆安排的會面，與C朗加盟祖雲達斯的傳聞有關。<br />\n<br />\n近日祖雲達斯欲羅致基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）的消息傳得熱烘烘，據悉轉會費接近1億英鎊！西班牙傳媒報道，其經理人文迪斯已急赴馬德里與會長佩雷斯見面，顯然是將傾談C朗的去留。據悉，C朗不滿佩雷斯沒能遵守加薪續約的承諾，因此打算離隊他投。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《馬卡報》還重溫C朗4月接受訪問時的内容，當時C朗說：「當我還是小孩的時候，一直喜歡祖雲達斯。」當時，他在歐聯作客施展倒掛攻破祖記大門，當時主隊球迷替他鼓掌歡呼，令他不禁説出自己的小秘密。<br />\n<br />\n到底，C朗是真心想加盟自小就心儀的祖雲達斯，還是借助對方向佩雷斯施壓，從而達到加薪續約的目的？不久將來便有答案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a8c53fd0c65f8873c17f8c31c1648c1027f789","tid":730469,"uid":33799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"前祖雲達斯CEO莫吉表示，在C朗還年輕時已經想把他帶到祖雲達斯，並相信老婦人已經跟C朗簽約。<br />\n<br />\n傳C朗投祖雲 馬度迪：望與世上最佳合作<br />\n<br />\n有傳祖記以1億歐元簽入C朗，在1994-2006年間任祖雲達斯CEO的莫治表示，接觸過相關重要人物後，相信C朗已經通過體測並簽約。<br />\n<br />\n莫吉還表示在2002年他已打算用沙拉斯換當時仍效力士砵亭的C朗。<br />\n<br />\n「我收到風，所以派人去觀察C朗，當時他18歲，但就表現得十分成熟。」<br />\n<br />\n「我已準備好合約，但沙拉斯拒絕去士砵亭，因為他想返回河床。我開出500萬去簽C朗，但最終不成功。」"},{"pid":"e9190327cb5284b1f81427167b52150f0b1da852","tid":730469,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"牙朗真係去祖記？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0372ef5b282f3335fd8290474f010e82be28efc","tid":730469,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"賓周馬變希古恩"},{"pid":"10c756a035116c3b13b4e12717008e09cf7bd7de","tid":730469,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97d1dd0c293140f7bd45a6af6ee7cfed7feb46d5","tid":730469,"uid":128014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"左有杜格拉斯，右有戴巴拿，c朗可以放心打中鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa0dfd214346fe6f6c633e27c061c52e38bafbc","tid":730469,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c756a035116c3b13b4e12717008e09cf7bd7de","tid":730469,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"加埋大巴拿條鋒線勁到痴左線"},{"pid":"73a6adc108ab7408b7ffb64bfbe905910fbc239b","tid":730469,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"國內是旦打都贏<br />\n<br />\n全力戰歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef609f080cf639a5e3ad1b45f45c04c48cacd6d","tid":730469,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/204615_19b8193a617e34f063ab652e164a6a6c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F204615_19b8193a617e34f063ab652e164a6a6c.png&h=06bd5666&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"104658e0797e43ccb9a2a668f222e9cd703a1c56","tid":730469,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"祖記一直都爭個踢歐聯決賽唔會怯場既人"}]}